an java application for word anagram 

Usage:
1.run application
git clone https://github.com/LiYunhaooooooo/word-anagram-solver.git
cd word-anagram-solver
./runme.sh

2.replace dictionary and input
enter resource and replace words.txt with wanted dictionary file
change value for dictionary in config.properties file

enter resource and replace input.txt with wanted input file
change value for input in config.properties file

Idea:
Build a tireTree for a dictionay 
for input array set , search every character in tiretree by dfs
if all the characters are used and the node in tireTree is an end , the corresponding word is added

Test:
the application is tested by Junit test
more test case can be added into resorce/test

have fun